// RAG Engineering Assistant — Ground-Truth Test Set
// Format: one JSON object per line (JSONL)
// query_type: "in_corpus" | "borderline" | "out_of_corpus"
//
// TARGET: 30 queries total — ~20 in_corpus, ~5 borderline, ~5 out_of_corpus
// BUILD THESE MANUALLY during Phase 2 after documents are ingested.
// Each query must be answerable from a specific page of a specific document.
//
// Fields:
//   query                    — the natural-language question
